imdb.plot outline: By increasing your strength and metabolism, Cardio Burn Walking for Weight Loss helps you lose weight fast. Created and guided by award-winning certified fitness instructor Madeleine Lewis, this unique walking fitness workout program shows you how to boost the fat- and calorie-burning power of fitness walking and fit it into your schedule.
